{"tid":342422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信報：李小加去信積金局　倡 MPF 可加碼買A股","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T01:21:43.000Z","uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a62a7a50d240b4c01d20b13e06a1eeda78b495","tid":342422,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"《信報》今日頭版引述消息指出，港交所行政總裁李小加把握時機去信強積金管理局，促請局方把A股市場納入可供強積金（MPF）投資的「核准港外證券交易所名單」（MPF核准名單）。<br />\n<br />\n港交所發言人回應報道時稱，不評論市場傳聞。根據強積金條例（第485章）第III部的核准交易所指引，目前共有33個國家或地區的交易所獲列入MPF核准名單，當中並未包括A股；條例指出，投資非核准範圍資產的比例，最多不能超過10%，故此目前MPF若要投資A股，規模限於有關比例。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，李小加此舉是希望讓基金界推出佔A股比重較大的MPF產品，為打工仔提供更多選擇；二來有利港交所日後與內地洽商中港互聯互通合作時，有更多談判籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%80-%E5%80%A1-mpf-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E8%B2%B7a%E8%82%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2580%25A1-mpf-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7a%25E8%2582%25A1%2F&d=7xwA1LCTBZptFpxobPm7rozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4965e8eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2580%25A1-mpf-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7a%25E8%2582%25A1%2F&h=deb8455c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%80-%E5%80%A1-mpf-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E8%B2%B7a%E8%82%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba98336edf9b90840740e2efd3abbeae8720a6dc","tid":342422,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c540fad665af8aa9be98a81f6264d8078ec127a5","tid":342422,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"冚家high high high 李小加佢正仆街"},{"pid":"0f4cab44b99a2fa076375eab366967bb975209a3","tid":342422,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"李小加老母已經夠忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f54a29895362283a4e38b134cf6846cce7ca8cf","tid":342422,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"等於借錢俾中國 一去不返"},{"pid":"57e0f114ac0cc5cab4612cc1734a8e2fdce2ff8c","tid":342422,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"0051f74702c6b4da099e73e15b272a1e39c4f5aa","tid":342422,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"大陸人有乜資格對港說三道四?"},{"pid":"774ef49e1f6f8588d79500765e78866a063fdb96","tid":342422,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:21:43.000Z","msg":"支那人咁有錢 洗乜要香港人錢"}]}